# makeIterator()

**Instance Method**

Returns an iterator over the elements of the collection.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor @preconcurrency func makeIterator() -> Scene.AnchorCollection.Iterator
```

## Iterating over the collection

- **Scene.AnchorCollection.Iterator**: An iterator that presents the elements of the collection.
- **Scene.AnchorCollection.Element**: The type of element traversed by the iterator.
